\
13. President Donald Trump froze disbursement of Inflation Reduction Act and Bipartisan Infrastructure Act funds (2025-01-23): By suspending funding for major infrastructure and clean\uc0\u8209 energy programs, Trump asserted executive control over congressionally appropriated spending, testing limits on presidential impoundment of funds.\
\
14. President Donald Trump used executive orders to direct investigations into alleged weaponization and censorship by the prior administration (2025-01-20): Trump\'92s orders instructing DOJ and intelligence leaders to probe supposed past \'93weaponization\'94 and censorship risked turning investigative powers into tools for revisiting political grievances.\
\
