21. National Security Counselors and allied plaintiffs filed suit alleging the DOGE program violated federal transparency rules (2025-01-20): Litigation claiming DOGE functions as an unregulated federal advisory committee challenged the administration\'92s attempt to run a powerful policy shop without standard public\uc0\u8209 access and record\u8209 keeping safeguards.\
